Recipe:
 Boil the chicken breast, adding salt. Hard-boil the eggs. Chop the chicken breast and eggs. Grate the cheese. Blend all dressing ingredients in a blender.
 Arrange in layers on lettuce leaves:
 - chicken;
 - croutons;
 - eggs;
 - cheese;
 - cherry tomatoes.
 Pour the prepared sauce over everything and sprinkle with freshly ground pepper.
